programList.comment: Greetings, captain
of the starship

programList.value: Glad you've finally woken up! You banged your head quite badly there and we were worried that your central processing unit was severely damaged, but it seems that you're fine enough to open your eyes! Wonderful. How do you feel?
programList.comment: Glad you've finally woken up! You banged your head quite badly there and we were worried that your central processing unit was severely damaged, but it seems that you're fine enough to open your eyes! Wonderful. How do you feel?

programList.value: Hey, you don't mind giving me some ships, please?

programList.comment: Sure, captain! Added
Pkunk vessels to your fleet!

programList.value: Looks like your fleet is already full and there's no slots left!
programList.comment: Looks like your fleet is already full and there's no slots left!

programList.value: Oh! Right, sorry. "brain" you call it, I think. Funny word. Sounds almost fake, if you ask me.
programList.comment: Oh! Right, sorry. "brain" you call it, I think. Funny word. Sounds almost fake, if you ask me.

programList.value: Hey! What are those glowy bits inside you?
Ah, those are a private matter to us. Please don't ask about our glowy bits ever again, thanks.
programList.comment: Ah, those are a private matter to us. Please don't ask about our glowy bits ever again, thanks.

programList.value:
Well, we were zipping around space in our awesome spaceship, when we randomly stumbled upon your nice planet.
Our pilot figured it'd be great to land on your world, and we did!
Or, well, we tried to.
See, the thing is, our spaceship is rather difficult to control in atmospheres as thick as around your world.
..and... well...
We happened to accidentally veer widely off course and land RIGHT on top of your parked spaceship.
Sorry about that!

programList.value: Err... Spaceship? I don't have a spaceship. You mean my car?
"Car"? Is that what you call spaceships?
programList.comment: "Car"? Is that what you call spaceships?

programList.value: No; cars are something different entirely. They're on wheels. We don't have spaceships; not really at least.
You don't have spaceships!? Wow! How do you people even get to space?
programList.comment: You don't have spaceships!? Wow! How do you people even get to space?

programList.value: We don't go to space. Well, not really. Most of us don't. Some do. It's complicated.
Oh, I see this bothers you.
programList.comment: Oh, I see this bothers you.

programList.value: Just like our glowy bits bother us when you ask about it.
programList.comment: Just like our glowy bits bother us when you ask about it.

programList.value: We won't mention cars again. Sorry.
programList.comment: We won't mention cars again. Sorry.

programList.value: We are the Humsters. We're intergalactical space travellers! Awesome, huh?
programList.comment: We are the Humsters. We're intergalactical space travellers! Awesome, huh?

programList.value: "Humsters"? That's a bit of a weird name. Sounds familiar.
Yeah, some other humanoid-like creature gave it to us. We don't really know why.
programList.comment: Yeah, some other humanoid-like creature gave it to us. We don't really know why.

programList.value: Oh, no. You're called "Humsters" because you're like Hamsters and like cheese!?
Huh? "Hamsters"? That name sounds just like ours... What are "Hamsters"? Are they also intergalactical space travellers!? We'd love to get to meet more advanced species that also travel across space!
programList.comment: Huh? "Hamsters"? That name sounds just like ours... What are "Hamsters"? Are they also intergalactical space travellers!? We'd love to get to meet more advanced species that also travel across space!

programList.value: What are you doing in our solar system?
We're just travelling and looking for cheese.
programList.comment: We're just travelling and looking for cheese.
Yeah, we love cheese!
Goodbye, human!
Wow, they sound amazing!

programList.value: Oh, look at my watch, it's time to go. Goodbye!

What is a watch?
Oh... You are already gone.
Well, goodbye then.
programList.comment:
What is a watch?
Oh... You are already gone.
Well, goodbye then.

programList.value: Can you tell us more about hamsters please?
programList.comment: Can you tell us more about hamsters please?
We have soft hair!
We have cute eyes!
We have a fuzzy tail!

programList.value: Hamsters are great at running in wheels

WE ARE GREAT AT RUNNING IN WHEELS!
Wow, Human! It seems that we just discovered something AWESOME.
WE. ARE. HAMSTERS!
Not Humsters!
Wow!

programList.comment: Wow, I'm sure!

programList.value: Sure is! I'm glad we managed to figure that out, Human!
